<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/baroness-anderson-of-stoke-on-trent> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Baroness Anderson of Stoke-on-Trent was appointed Baroness in Waiting (Government Whip) on 11 July 2024. She was appointed as Parliamentary Secretary in the Cabinet Office on 3 March 2026."@en .
